{"tid":616523,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] King’s Raid #104 又係時候曬命","createTime":"2018-04-04T08:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T08:34:21.000Z","uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e58f35c0528b384ec6640ee0ddf3b0de219dda10","tid":616523,"uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:33:23.000Z","msg":"[center]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Server【Japan】</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png&h=72e0e3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩新手巴絲睇咗全攻略先，睇完有咩唔明再問，所有攻略僅供參考</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【LIHKG】King's Raid 全攻略</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>【日服連登公會】 </strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新手巴絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>亂入公會，要入就入Lihkg公會<br />\n因為你一入錯，要退會入Lihkg公會，就要等足七日先會有奬勵你拎<br />\n唔使問有無位，搵到即係有，搵唔到即係無<br />\n申請咗邊個公會+ID麻煩填表，優先處理填表巴絲<br />\n填完麻煩再係Post度留名話自己填咗表，即有專人為你服務</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只限日服適用 - 刷首抽Q&amp;A</strong></span></span><br />\n所有Q&amp;A僅供參考，各巴絲可自行選擇有愛之英雄作為目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：點解我無得抽嘅？</span><br />\nA：麻煩出Game再入Game睇下自己揀咗咩Ser，目前只有日服先會有得刷廿抽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：點樣拎廿抽？</span><br />\nA：打完頭三關教學任務，去右上角信箱拎石同十抽卷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：抽邊個Pool好？點解？</span><br />\nA：首推刺客Pool<br />\n因為每隻英都會有個人專用嘅<br />\nUW = Unique Weapon <br />\nUT = Unique Treasure<br />\n兩樣係唔同嘅裝備，裝嘅位置唔一樣，可以同時使用，將隻英發揮到最大嘅效果<br />\n因為有52隻英，咁就唔一一貼上嚟<br />\n<br />\n全英雄Skill、UT、UW、Artifact整合英文版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com/?item=Kasel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaskofgoblin.netlify.com%2F%3Fitem%3DKasel&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=624fd504\" target=\"_blank\">https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com/?item=Kasel</a><br />\n<br />\n全英雄Skill、UW整合殘體中文版：(非最新版本，所以麻煩連埋第一頁全攻略嚟睇)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067&amp;rand=824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D12943067%26rand%3D824&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1a7c1199\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067&amp;rand=824</a><br />\n<br />\n全英雄UT殘體中文版：(如果唔知佢講啲英係邊隻去上面全人物圖鑑對/直接問)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=13705992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D13705992&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b6df0aff\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=13705992</a>"},{"pid":"81bb30148fab60fc98dc3bf663849fc4f2526fb0","tid":616523,"uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">刺客Pool原因：</span><br />\n入面有幾把unique weapon(uw) 同unique treasure(ut)都比較勁<br />\n不過最重要係有愛&gt;一切，抽其他pool都得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：抽到咩先開局？</span><br />\nA:如果你係跟大圍抽刺客Pool的話<br />\n抽中Mirianne既UW/UT，Roi既UW/UT，Epis既UW/UT，都推介大家開局<br />\n同埋建議係UT&gt;UW，因為UW 15日會送自選劵，但UT暫時係無劵可以自選，最多隨機<br />\n但52隻英幾時先會中到你想要嗰隻...<br />\n如果巴絲唔肯定開局與否請上嚟問我哋<br />\n都係嗰句，有愛就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：如何刪帳重刷？</span><br />\nA：1：撳左上角個頭像<br />\n2：Others<br />\n3：Leave<br />\n4：之後打句【I agree to delete my account】就搞掂<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/200034_a35f6a580aa96407913fd1a390b58af5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F200034_a35f6a580aa96407913fd1a390b58af5.jpg&h=421ef0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">謹記<br />\n將方法將會刪除帳號內資料<br />\n所以真係棄先好打</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家刷到好開局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/center]"},{"pid":"7c5cfe434f0a260cc5e90ff7c812b4a2aae0b01c","tid":616523,"uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Server【Asia】</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F141711_dedcc7b9deea6af5d8691a925b55be6f.png&h=72e0e3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ANDROID</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F4943&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c4bdfbb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/4943</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IOS</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/u