src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[center]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nQ：英雄自選劵揀咩英好?<br />\nA：有愛&gt;一切<br />\n依隻驚無勁唔勁，只有夾唔夾<br />\n同埋官方會因應英雄強弱而作出Buff同Nerf嘅調整<br />\n今個版本可能弱勢啲，但下個版本可能變神角都未定<br />\n所以不如揀咗有邊隻英係你真係鍾意嘅，想用嘅<br />\n再係Post度問下有咩組合可以夾佢，咁會比較好<br />\n相信各巴絲都好樂意為新手巴絲們解答的<br />\n<br />\nQ：我抽到依樣嘢又唔係專武，咁係咩嚟?<br />\nA：Artifact"},{"pid":"7a6dbf1f14e4bc43ab9d2e6aa7ac25d214b6e8d4","tid":616523,"uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"英文版：<a href=\"https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaskofgoblin.netlify.com&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=de792ed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com</a><br />\n殘中版：<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D12943067&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=31e8ba48\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/225213_b0ebf846580f6d4fd30174af7c4c201d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F225213_b0ebf846580f6d4fd30174af7c4c201d.jpg&h=70b636b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：需唔需要刷首抽架？<br />\nA：無首抽依回事，因為唔係抽返嚟，係可以直接用英雄自選卷換返嚟(新英除外)<br />\n【新手一定會有一張二星同三星英雄自選劵】<br />\n<br />\n如有更多問題可詳見【LIHKG】King's Raid 全攻略<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/center]"},{"pid":"199d56d2a1e4a71e3e424d194c51d3f96270379f","tid":616523,"uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f8bd19154b626b65f64238b671823632d49053d9","tid":616523,"uid":2